OL,3,CMan, 41, lost leg after excavator
OL,4,Creverses into him at work
OL,6,FA waste and recycling company has been
OL,7,Ffined more than #100,000 after an
OL,8,Femployee lost his leg while working.
OL,10,FThe 41-year-old man had been sorting
OL,11,Frefuse with two other staff members at
OL,12,Fthe Levenshulme site of Pink Skips
OL,13,F(NW) Ltd in Manchester, on 5 October
OL,14,F2022 when the incident happened.
OL,16,FA 360-excavator was being used to move
OL,17,Fwaste in the same area that the group
OL,18,Fwas working.
