OL,3,CMan, 41, lost leg after excavator
OL,4,Creverses into him at work
OL,6,FAs one of the men was standing behind
OL,7,Fthe vehicle, it suddenly reversed,
OL,8,Fstriking him, and running over his leg.
OL,10,FThe injury was so severe the leg had
OL,11,Fto be amputated above the knee. The
OL,12,FRomanian father and grandfather has
OL,13,Fbeen left unable to work and still
OL,14,Fsuffers from considerable pain.
OL,16,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,17,FSafety Executive (HSE) found that Pink
OL,18,FSkips (NW) Ltd had failed to
OL,19,Fadequately segregate pedestrians and
OL,20,Fvehicles.
