OL,3,CMan, 41, lost leg after excavator
OL,4,Creverses into him at work
OL,6,FThe investigation also found that hand
OL,7,Fpicking regularly occurred around the
OL,8,Fexcavator operating.
OL,10,FThere was a written safe system of
OL,11,Fwork which stated that operatives were
OL,12,Fnot to work within the swing reach
OL,13,Farea of the excavator, that barriers
OL,14,Fshould be placed between operatives
OL,15,Fand machines at all times, and that
OL,16,Fbanksmen should be used.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
