OL,3,CMan, 41, lost leg after excavator
OL,4,Creverses into him at work
OL,6,FAfter the hearing HSE inspector Lisa
OL,7,FBailey said: "The company failed to
OL,8,Fsegregate pedestrians and vehicles or
OL,9,Fput in place a safe system of work for
OL,10,Fits hand sorting and picking
OL,11,Factivities, thereby exposing
OL,12,Femployees, to the risk of being struck
OL,13,Fby workplace vehicles.
OL,15,F"The injuries sustained here have been
OL,16,Ftruly life-changing."
